text: I wanted to take this opportunity to wish all my Jewish friends and their families a Happy and Healthy Passover! May the spirit of liberation from slavery be a reminder of God’s mercy and recognition of our ancestors’ suffering.

For all, let Freedom reign amidst a world that needs recovery from the Covid pandemic as we begin to see some vaccine lights at the end of the tunnel. This holiday provides us the great opportunity to appreciate our families and the good things we have versus the often less
